title: Costa Rica Rainforest
description:
Welcome to episode 001 of the Sleep & Relax ASMR podcast! Today's intro episode is all about gentle whispering over a serene Costa Rica rainforest. I'll go into a bit about myself, what to expect from the podcast, and more. This is great for getting into a nice deep state of relaxation, and/or falling asleep!
